@startuml
title GRIDBOT - Diagrama Conceptual
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor Administrador
actor Operador

rectangle "Frontend" {
  component "Panel Administrador\nReact + Vite" as AdminUI
  component "Panel Operador\nReact + Vite" as OperatorUI
}

rectangle "Capa de Aplicación" {
  component "Backend GRIDBOT\nNode.js + Express" as Backend
  component "API REST" as Api
  component "Socket.IO" as Socket
}

rectangle "Comunicación MQTT" {
  component "Broker MQTT\nMosquitto" as Broker
  component "Emulador MQTT Externo" as Emulator
}

rectangle "Persistencia" {
  database "PostgreSQL\nPrisma ORM" as Database
}

cloud "Docker / Demo LAN" as DemoLan

Administrador --> AdminUI : Usa panel central
Operador --> OperatorUI : Usa panel operativo

AdminUI --> Api : Solicitudes HTTP REST
OperatorUI --> Api : Solicitudes HTTP REST

AdminUI --> Socket : Eventos y actualizaciones
OperatorUI --> Socket : Eventos y actualizaciones

Api --> Backend : Controladores y lógica
Socket --> Backend : Tiempo real bidireccional

Backend --> Database : Lee / escribe datos
Backend --> Broker : Publica y se suscribe

Broker --> Emulator : Comandos MQTT
Emulator --> Broker : Status / Telemetry

Broker --> Backend : Mensajes MQTT
Backend --> Socket : Estado en tiempo real

DemoLan --- AdminUI
DemoLan --- OperatorUI
DemoLan --- Backend
DemoLan --- Broker
DemoLan --- Database
DemoLan --- Emulator

note bottom of Backend
Centraliza la lógica del sistema:
- robots
- tareas
- operadores
- rutas
- validaciones
- histórico
end note

note right of Broker
Canales principales:
- gridbot/robots/{robotId}/commands
- gridbot/robots/{robotId}/status
- gridbot/robots/{robotId}/telemetry
- gridbot/tasks/events
end note

note bottom of Database
Persistencia de:
- tareas
- robots
- operadores
- eventos históricos
- telemetría
end note

@enduml
